=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你宮崎預鬆少少時間好過啦</blockquote><br />\n岩岩睇宮崎去高千既巴士得星期六日有 仲要一日得一班 時間唔夾 要放棄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074719786e1a4ad84b2e46e55af7c0dba1b77a1b","tid":374060,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:04:59.000Z","msg":"華蓮好普通, 而且少少貴, 你考慮下食唔食好<br />\n<br />\n宮崎牛間間都正, 但大淀河畔一定比APAS好好多"},{"pid":"82800ba437e85f826effb9b237d12eed8e6ab72d","tid":374060,"uid":14554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>華蓮好普通, 而且少少貴, 你考慮下食唔食好<br />\n<br />\n宮崎牛間間都正, 但大淀河畔一定比APAS好好多</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c444a965eb8da5d1a483895a0532bd89f0dc0f0a","tid":374060,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"高千穗峽未去都聞到陣伏味<br />\n山長水遠去到打個卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4bd61ad68eacfd3eeccf6c6632759ef6c4e4b4","tid":374060,"uid":14554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高千穗峽未去都聞到陣伏味<br />\n山長水遠去到打個卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7731794f0ab04d06cbe95f3f5ad397dc0597ee8f","tid":374060,"uid":14554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:40:03.000Z","msg":"改一改左行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 坐HKA 4點到鹿兒島機場 -&gt; 鹿兒島中央check in -&gt; 屋台村 [住鹿兒島]<br />\nDay 2: 櫻島 -&gt; 仙嚴園 -&gt; 天文館附近行/食  [住鹿兒島]<br />\nDay 3: 指宿 - (長崎鼻/開聞岳/龍宮神社)       [住鹿兒島]<br />\nDay 4: 霧島 - (神話之里公園+丸尾瀑布+霧島神宮)   [住鹿兒島]<br />\nDay 5: 宮崎 - 青島(青島神社+鬼之洗衣板) 日南(鵜戶神宮)  [住宮崎]<br />\nDay 6: 早船去屋久島       [住屋久島]<br />\nDay 7: 尾班船返鹿兒島   [住鹿兒島]<br />\nDay 8: 唔知做咩?? -&gt; 下午5點機返香港"},{"pid":"80c804be044ee42c0add3909bfef806c898ddc8e","tid":374060,"uid":51636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:05:21.000Z","msg":"屋久島咁短時間諗住行哂繩文衫同太鼓岩？<br />\n仲未預有機會落雨<br />\n霧島留返尾二日住，直接搭去機場又近啲"}]}